
**a form of panegyric poem generally in akaval metre in which one who has been rewarded with gifts directs another to the presence of the chief from whom the latter may also receive similar reward**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   ஆற்றுப்படை
-


**a man who directs the supervisors of a king**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   கருமவிதிகள்
-


**form of panegyric poem generally in agaval metre in which the poet who has been rewarded with gifts directs another poet to the chief from whom the latter**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   ஆற்றுப்படை
-


**theme in which a viali who had been rewarded by a king directs another viali to the royal presence to obtain rewards**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   விறலியாற்றுப்படை
-


**theme in which a who had been rewarded by a king directs another to the royal presence to obtain rewards**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   விறலியாற்றுப்படை
